Detailed Description

The CollisionDetector checks the scenegraphs BoundingVolume heirarchy for collisions.

The collision detection algorithm used requires the scenegraph to be ordered with leaf nodes on the left of non-leaf nodes.

THIS COLLISION DETECTOR CAN ONLY BE USED WITH 3D SCENEGRAPHS.

Author:
Ben Constable, original Java code by Oli Winks
Version:
1.0
